packaging list and COO (Country of Origin)certification in your shipping documents.对于海外业务,出货文件中请包含样件订单,发票,包装和原产国证明。7.For domestic suppliers,if ETA is on 1st-19th,please download goods receiving record from LIS andcreate invoice in the same month. If ETA is on 20th-31st,please download goods receiving record fromLIS and create invoice next month. Goods receiving record updated date in LIS is on 20th-22nd of every month.The PO will be closed in ALV system and can&#x27;t be paid if not meet the requirement.对于国内业务,到货日在1日-19日,请确保当月从LIS系统下载对账单并开据发票。到货日在20日到31日的,请确保次月之内从LIS系统下载对账单并开据发票。对账日为每月的20日到22日。如不及时处理,系统内将关闭此订单,付款将不能被处理。</td></tr></table>",
